data.description: Great opportunity with this 4 bed, 3 full bathroom ranch home sitting on 4.65 acres.  IF you like garages/pole barns...this is the place for you!! This home features a beautiful addition with master suite, walk-out lower level, over 3000 sq ft, and huge deck. There is a spacious three car attached garage, large 40x60 pole barn with an office / bathroom, and a small pole barn to keep all your toys and equipment in. Cathedral ceilings in the living room with a fireplace to enjoy on those cold winter nights and skylights to enjoy the natural light This company makes no warranty or representations about the contents of this data. It is the responsibility of the parties looking at the property to satisfy themselves as to the accuracy of this information. Taxes were obtained from the local assessor and the taxes could change for the buyer after a closed transaction.
